<p><i><b>Photo Production Ltd v Securicor Transport Ltd</b></i> [1980] <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.bailii.org/uk/cases/UKHL/1980/2.html">UKHL 2</a> is an <a href="/wiki/English_contract_law" title="English contract law">English contract law</a> case decided by the <a href="/wiki/Judicial_functions_of_the_House_of_Lords" title="Judicial functions of the House of Lords">House of Lords</a> on construction of a contract and the doctrine of <a href="/wiki/Fundamental_breach" title="Fundamental breach">fundamental breach</a>.</p>
<p></p>
<div id="toc" class="toc">
<div id="toctitle">
